    <p class="description">The use of software to execute business processes automatically based on triggers and rules, eliminating repetitive manual work. In marketing, workflow automation handles <strong>email sequences, lead routing, CRM updates, and social publishing</strong> — turning hours of manual effort into zero-touch operations that run 24/7.</p>
