            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Common tools include Zapier and Make (Integromat) for no-code cross-app automation, HubSpot and Marketo for marketing-specific workflows, n8n for open-source self-hosted automation, and native automation features in CRMs like Salesforce. Enterprise workflows often use platforms like Microsoft Power Automate or Workato.</p></div></div>
          </div>
